    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Barrow-draugr are ancient undead disinterred from Svellheim's cairns — skeletal forms of rusted metal and tattered leather, their eye sockets burning with pale cold light. They move with jerking, unnatural gaits and emanate bitter cold. Their rune-blade strikes carry cursed frost that lingers in wounds, and their calcified grasps can restrain even powerful warriors. They are the backbone of the undead host's assault formations.</p>",
